# ScholarAIO Cursor Rules (Legacy)

Cursor's current native project-rule entry, checked against official Cursor
rules documentation on 2026-04-10, is `.cursor/rules/scholaraio.mdc`. This
legacy `.cursorrules` file is kept only for older Cursor versions.

Read `.cursor/rules/scholaraio.mdc` first, then read `AGENTS.md` for the full
project instructions. Use `.claude/skills/*/SKILL.md` as reusable workflows and
`scholaraio --help` as the CLI entry point.
